controller.editor

Class GridEditorImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.editor.GridEditorImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GridEditor, PatternEditor

    public class GridEditorImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements GridEditor, PatternEditor
    GridEditorImpl is the editor for the grid and the pattern manager depending on which interface is used; it allows to perform changes to the view of the grid.
